        {
            "name": "Goliath Spider",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [],
            "text": "Goliath spiders dwell in the deepest jungles, where they build webs as big as temples and feast on prey as large as hippopotami.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Animal</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 28",
